      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PRINCESS ADA (7) could manage only third at Wentworth Park last time but turned heads when clocking a head turning 29.58 over 520m at this track three starts ago. Rates a top chance if runs up to time three back. GIGGLE HAT (4) comes here off a placing in quick time (24.85) over 440m at Goulburn. Expecting another bold showing. ZIPPING RAPUNZEL (2) was strongly fancied latest and proved too good with a neck win at this track in a handy 29.92. Fair draw can see a good run and goes well over this trip. Yet to score from this box but has never missed the frame in three starts. Must be included in calculations. TERRY TANGLES (1) is in the mix despite missing out at this track last time.",
